name: CakeMix
description:
an anime model which is clean, colorful, 3d depth feeling.

Recommend download version 3 or 4 because It is close to the style I want to get for this model.

Painting with anime face instead of anime painting

If you add some tag like photorealistic, realistic, you will get doll, 3d game like style.

Compatible with wide range of styles lora.

Can get anime flatness with bad prompt embedding

the VAE is already baked in the model

modelVersions.name: v4.0
modelVersions.description:
Skin is smoother and better, face is more 3d (but still anime).

better hands
